##Further help##

^If you can't meet your mortgage repayments, or you are worried you might fall behind -  talk to your lender first^

You can get further information about mortgage arrears or payment difficulties from the [National Homelessness Advice Service](http://www.nhas.org.uk/index.htm "National Homelessness Advice Service"){:rel="external"} or the [Money Advice Service.](http://www.moneyadviceservice.org.uk "the Money Advice Service"){:rel="external"}

You can also get independent advice from other organisations, eg [Citizens Advice Bureau.](http://www.citizensadvice.org.uk/cabdir.ihtml#txt_getadvice_header-Anchor-search "Find your local Citizens Advice Bureau"){:rel="external"} 

*[SMI]: Support for Mortgage Interest
